{"tid":1735104,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【集思廣益】我建議 復課就即刻重啟黎明行動！","createTime":"2019-11-18T13:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T14:41:26.000Z","uid":205482,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6e90a860f0ce57c6d6986e990c399f6d42707d00","tid":1735104,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:08:05.000Z","msg":"利申借ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家黎討論</span></strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>黎明行動成功之處</strong></span><br />\n黎明行動喺今次運動中<span style=\"color: red;\">突破瓶頸喺無可置疑嘅</span><br />\n成功<span style=\"color: red;\">令學校幾乎全面癱瘓 港豬遲翻工</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">黎明行動目前困境</span></strong><br />\n1. 港豬提早翻工<br />\n2. 停課 無咗學生幫手塞<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">撞上Poly大屠殺 令焦點不再喺黎明行動</span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n所以我個人嘅建議喺<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">等全港學校復課 即刻重啟黎明行動</span><br />\n一黎<span style=\"color: violet;\">比poly果邊有緩衝時間</span><br />\n二黎<span style=\"color: violet;\">有幫學生幫手塞 成效更大</span><br />\n結合依兩點 令黎明行動可以延續 對政府造成傷害<br />\n<br />\n我地要實現<span style=\"color: red;\">不完美 可改善</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當行動<span style=\"color: red;\">有效但有缺陷</span><br />\n應該<span style=\"color: red;\">揾改善方法 試多幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n而唔喺一下就話<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好繼續做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">我知大家依家情緒好激動<br />\n不過希望大家討論時保持理性&amp;冷靜<br />\n大家都喺想場運動贏 何必動氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"af9ef8d143972a24d59dadf573a5d225ab4daed8","tid":1735104,"uid":205482,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:09:49.000Z","msg":"請幫手推下 等人入黎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗則不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9484b922e7567f4bfeb90d2de2fc213ab96d969f","tid":1735104,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab2f032fada4e121e5c5b26aacd531f49743803","tid":1735104,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c2fdfd13809056b819b1c5e955a48a88ec1585","tid":1735104,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:10:45.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd391cca3e549cc91c126668f403d990249ad0e","tid":1735104,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a503c47aaa458520e42e4cdeb0ce1e318d3f94","tid":1735104,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e6acbe3acd9ac0345251b1a67ea20bdf50cb5a","tid":1735104,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef740ffefccc46c5b44783ea57fa72046e0ab7c4","tid":1735104,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9de81385539846396d02fe54762f62beb17615","tid":1735104,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc